Plan written to `plan-issue-32.json`. Here's a quick overview:

**3 files** to modify:
- `page.tsx` — inline stats grid → `StatCard`, inline header → `PageHeader`
- `layout.tsx` — inline header → `PageHeader`
- `meetings-app.tsx` — the bulk of the work:
  - All inline `<span>` badges → `Badge` (sentiment, client, duration, priority, topics)
  - Inline `<button>` elements → `Button` (follow-up, mark done)
  - Inline `<input>` fields → `Search` component
  - Inline filter button groups → `PillList` (date range, status, priority)
  - Inline empty-state divs → `EmptyState`

The plan follows the same migration pattern used in the Standup app (Badge with variant="outline" + color className overrides, shared layout components).